highlights.description: 🇨🇳Chinese center Yang Hansen, who turns 20 this Thursday, enters the #NBA after two standout seasons with the Qingdao Eagles in the #CBA. 🔥During the 2024-25 regular season, he averaged 16.6 points, 10.5 rebounds, 3.0 assists, and 2.6 blocks per game. #NBADraft

The Trail Blazers improve their record to 1-0 with the win, while the Warriors fall to 0-1.
